{
  "stem": "14552.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was-- I was-- I only overheard while they were talking the next day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't help it, because children will hear through thick walls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the fear was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Constant fear.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were those [? chanters. ?] They were the peacekeepers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had those rooster feathers on their helmet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they came around, you could see them from the window that their feather was going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then you knew that they're out for trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're going to do something destructive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were very, very poorly behaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were very bad peasants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were given a gun, and authority, and go in to see what harm you can do to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And these peasants were very low on the human-- human chain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just went wild.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this went on for years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940. 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they would deport people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you would see the people taken off and beaten on the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just had-- they just had this-- let's punish, let's hurt, let's kill, let's loot because they are Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that constant fear, that constant pain, and that constant worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a mother to worry about her children which is so much-- so much harder for a mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a child is-- if you tell a child, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It will be OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A child will relax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A child will say, well OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mother knows best.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if she says it, that's what it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it never happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it was just-- it was just a time that you could not see the end of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then came in 1944 they took-- they had the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all I was-- I went to Czech school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
